title: The Mystery Room-PLAZA
description:
The Mystery Room (c) Moim

Release Date: 12/2017 Protection: Steam
Discs: 1 Genre: Adventure

This game is a game where you solve the puzzle problem and escape
the room. When you start the game, you will be able to solve the
puzzle problem and ask for reasoning ability. The protagonist
entered the house to experience horror and was trapped in the room
Every time you escape from a locked room, the story is revealed a
little bit. Play the game and find out what secrets are in the house
where the protagonist is trapped

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/727060/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
5. Play!
